The mapping tool, built in partnership with Development Gateway, allows users to select and layer any combination of CCAPS data onto one map to assess how myriad climate change impacts and responses intersect. By integrating the various lines of CCAPS research, as well as other existing datasets, the CCAPS mapping tool aims to provide the most comprehensive view yet of climate change and security in
